\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 And you just felt that you'd never do it again?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Did you feel resentful of your father for doing it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Oh no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Would you say that you received the 
ideas you had about how to behave from both your parents or did one play a more important part than the other?
