\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 No. No. Wouldn't have any parties or owt like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 You wouldn't have any presents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Oh yes, I - I occasionally got presents.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 From your parents would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Would you have anything special to eat at teatime perhaps?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 There'd be some cake - of some sort, you know, fruit cake or -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Would it be a birthday cake?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 With icing on and candles?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Yes - no candles, but icing, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 But you were never allowed to bring friends in for tea on your birthday, you never had any little guests to make a party of it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Not - not at that time, not until - pardon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 It would be much later would it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 How old would you be when you'd start having a party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 I think the first party I remember was me twenty-first. But - I'd take
n the - girl friend home - before that. And we started to - we started courting at seventeen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 But you never had an actual party when you were little?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Can you remember anything you did with your mother and father together on Christmas Day at all?
