Oh yes. We used to have a house party on the Sunday evening, and - move the - table down in the - kitchen. To - out of the way. And I - I've seen many a set of Lancers in - down in the kitchen.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 You'd dance the lancers, would there be some friends in as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Yes, some - some friends of mother and dad. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Was your father playing the piano then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Did your parents play games with you, either indoor or outdoor?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 The - card games. Mm.
