\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Oh yes, mm hm, he had about - we got them up h
ere when we - came up here, the second time, and we had a library here, and we used to let the people come and - pay - pay a penny - a time and borrow them. Mm. Oh was a wonderful selection.
