\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Yes. I remember one - went to - a boat trip on the canal. Aye. Mm. From the - from - Riddlesden to Farnhill. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Was it a barge that you went on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Oh yes, it was a coal barge.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 A horse pulling it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Yes. Uh huh.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 It sounds like a fairly enterprising sort of Sunday school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Oh yes, it was, mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 How often would you have these outings, would it be every year?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Oh mostly they'd arrange one every year. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 It was an annual event?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 When would it take place, during the summer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Yes. Mm hm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Not at a Bank Holiday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 
Not at - not at Bank Holiday. I remember one day - I was - there when they were - thanking - Mrs Bromborough - and - they wanted to know could they pay anything for - what they'd done. She says, no, if you line up and sing me a hymn I'll be satisfied Aye.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 That was the lady at White Hill Farm?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 At White Hill Farm. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Can you remember any other social activities that were organised by the church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Yes. Dan - dances. Oh social evenings and dances. And then they had the \{BLANK\} at the - Parish Church school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 What were those?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Fancy dress - on the Friday night and a - a ball on the Saturday. Oh used to always have to get a season ticket. Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 What was a season ticket, you went to both?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 For - for both, well, all t
hree. Because there were a kiddies party in the afternoon and we - we had to go to that to - help to organise it. And - then the ball at night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 This would be when you were getting a little bit older, in your teens?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Something like that. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 When you were still at school you would go to the party in the afternoon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 
Mm. Yes. Well I remember one time we went to a fancy dress ball. And - we'd no idea - my - girl had no idea what I was going as. As - and I had no idea what she were going at. 
But - she went as a colleen. Irish colleen. And I went as Irish gentleman. See, and I didn't know that.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 But that again would be when you were getting a bit older, you'd perhaps be fifteen or sixteen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Fif - sixteen. Well - when I'd started courting.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 You belonged to the choir, did the choir have any activities of its own, any outings or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 
We - we usually had one choir trip - during the - during the year, some - and - we went to Blackpool once or twice. And - meal was provided you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 You - went into a caf\'e9?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Yes. Uh huh.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 How would you get there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 
Went by train. And - one of the curate - the curate - Mr Hubbard - and - me uncle who was the - organist - took - supervised it. And then I - we had the Boy Scouts - from there as well. I joined the Boy Scouts when I was about - thirteen. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Did they have any trips out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Field days and the - flag days and that. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 What would they consist of, the field days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Well it - it was usually - a competit
ion between - one of the Bradford troops, and ours. And they'd - try to run a despatch into Keighley without us finding it. And they - they twisted us one day. They - sent a cyclist - out of uniform - with it, and it was - round one of the spokes of his -
 front wheel - taped on, and - so we never found it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Your troop would be host?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Yes. Uh huh.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Would you go back and they'd be host to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Mm hm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Did you belong to any other club organised by the church? You were a member of the Scouts?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Boy Scouts.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Was there anything else you remember, was there a temperance club at the church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Can you think of anything else that there was at the church besides the Scouts and choir?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 No I don't remember any - activities beyond that. Oh they had a - gymnastic team. Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Were you a member of it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 What did it do, was it just a matter of physical fitness or did you do displays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 We did displays. mm hm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Just at the church or would you go round doing displays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 If - if anyone invited us we'd go and give them. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 When you were at home was grace said before a meal or after a meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 On special occasions. Ah - Christ - Christmas dinner and such as that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Who would say it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Dad. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Were you taught to say prayers at night before you went to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Oh yes. Uh huh.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Did you ever have family prayers when you'd all pray together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Yes. Mm hm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 How often would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Well it wasn't a regular - affair, but when - when we were all - together sometimes we'd have them. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Did your father take an interest in politics? When you were a little boy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Do you know what his views were at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Oh he was a Con - Conservative.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Why did you think he held those views?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Pardon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Why do you think he held those views?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Because of - his own views. Of - to run things.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 He agreed with the Conservative party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Did your mother have any interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 She had - slight interest, not - very emphatical. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Would you know what her views were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Oh they - they were with his.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Why would she have her views, was it because she felt like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Or would it be that she agreed with your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Well, being - being in business - brought - you in contact with Conservative views. And - that - was what it de - developed from. Mm.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 So she tended to agree with your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Do you remember your father voting in a general election before 1919? I think there was an election in 1918.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Yes. Uh huh. Yes. Yes, I remember - and I remember me wearing the - rosette.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 What about your mother, she wouldn't get a vote until 1918.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Do you remember her using that vote in 1918?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Yes. Mm hm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 You remember her going to vote for the first time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Yes. Uh huh.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 In some places at that time men felt they risked losing their job or their house if they voted differently from their employe
rs, do you know if your father felt himself under that kind of pressure to vote for a particular party, that doesn't apply to you because obviously your father employed people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Would you say that the people he employed felt this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 No. No. He never brought any pressure to bear on - anyone, whether they were - I mean he'd argue with them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 He wouldn't try to influence them -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 From the position of an employer?
