\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Only the sport - school sports. - Aye. Running and - things - suchlike.
