\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Oh no. No. Spend that on sweets. Mm hm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Was it regular that money, did you get it ever Saturday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Was it always spent on sweets?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Yes. Uh huh.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16658231 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 Did anyone outside the home help your
 mother look after her house or family, other than Mrs Stevenson, did your mother have any friends or relatives or neighbours who would come in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517712 DF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 No.
