oked up to him. Mm. But his brother you know - he was the - our choirmaster, and after I'd - come out of the choir, he - used to - meet me in the mill, he used to come round of a - every morning, morning Fearnside. How did the choir go on on Sunday? And i
t depends}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458395\charrsid16474754  - sometimes he'd call me Danie}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2695593\charrsid16474754 
